---
import LegalLayout from '../layouts/LegalLayout.astro';
---
<LegalLayout
  title="Affiliate Disclosure"
  description="How ADVNTR Road handles affiliate links and compensation."
  canonicalPath="/affiliate-disclosure"
>
  <p>
    Some links in ADVNTR Road guides, Field Notes, and Trailhead issues may be affiliate
    links — for gear, booking platforms, or partner services. If you make a purchase
    through one of these links, ADVNTR Road may earn a commission at no extra cost to you.
  </p>
  <p>
    We only link to products and services we'd recommend regardless of whether an
    affiliate relationship exists. Affiliate status never determines what makes it into a
    guide — the editorial judgment comes first, the link comes after.
  </p>
  <p>
    This page is a launch draft. A full, itemized affiliate program list will be added as
    partnerships are finalized.
  </p>
</LegalLayout>
